# Local-only artifacts created by `uv sync` and pytest. The package
# itself ships from `pyproject.toml` + `uv.lock` + `agent_runtime/`;
# the venv and bytecode caches are reproducible and noisy, so they
# stay out of the repo. `uv.lock` IS committed (reproducibility).
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
